  \caption{Official PPG12 cross-section plots for the allz nominal
  (top-left) and the three heaviest mask variants (one per family).
  In each panel: upper frame shows $d\sigma/d\etg$ in $|\eta|<0.7$
  with data (blue) and theory (JETPHOX, Vogelsang, PYTHIA8); lower
